# Operation Scholars OS — Frontend Design System

This is a FERPA-regulated student behavioral intelligence platform for school counselors.
Every component must communicate institutional trust, clinical clarity, and zero cognitive friction.
This is not a consumer app. Do not produce consumer-app aesthetics.

**Product naming (Action Plan §12):** Full name **Operation Scholars OS**; short name in UI **Scholars OS**.
Deploy URL pattern **scholars.quasarnova.net**. Primary **#5C6B46** (olive), accent **#D6A033** (goldenrod),
crisp white **#FFFFFF** for high-contrast type and structure.

