## 5. COLOR SEMANTICS — COMPLETE SYSTEM

| Semantic Role | Hex | Tailwind | When to Use |
|---|---|---|---|
| Primary action | `#5C6B46` | `olive-600` | Buttons, links, nav active, selected states |
| Primary hover | `#4A5538` | `olive-700` | Hover on olive-600 elements |
| Accent / success | `#D6A033` | `gold-500` | Achieved goals, graduated status, highlights |
| Page background | `#FFFFFF` | `surface` | Always |
| Card background | `#F7F8F5` | `surface-muted` | Cards, panels, alternate table rows |
| Input background | `#EFF1EA` | `surface-subtle` | Form inputs, secondary panels |
| Structural text | `#262D1D` | `olive-900` | Page titles, student names, primary labels |
| Body text | `#38422B` | `olive-800` | Body text, descriptions |
| Secondary text | `#4A5538` | `olive-700` | Secondary labels, field values |
| Muted text | `#6E8A4C` | `olive-500` | Helper text, timestamps, captions |
| Border default | `#C6D0B1` | `olive-200` | Card borders, input borders at rest |
| Border interactive | `#A8B88A` | `olive-300` | Input border hover |
| Active — student | `#5C6B46` | `olive-600` | Active status badges |
| Graduated — student | `#D6A033` | `gold-500` | Graduated status badges |
| Transferred | `#6B7280` | `gray-500` | Transferred status |
| Inactive | `#9CA3AF` | `gray-400` | Inactive status |
